	pages={402-404},
	keywords={energy harvesting;integrated circuits;low-power electronics;optical communication;wireless sensor networks;application-specific implantable microsystems;die-stacked sensing platform;medical implants;multi-modal energy harvesting;optical communication;smart buildings;smart dust vision;surveillance systems;wireless sensor nodes;Batteries;Battery charge measurement;Biomedical measurements;Board of Directors;Phasor measurement units;Temperature measurement;Temperature sensors},
